    <title>手动为thunar增加x11光标缩略图支持</title>
    <link href="/2025/05/03/thunar-x11cursor-thumbnail/"/>
    <url>/2025/05/03/thunar-x11cursor-thumbnail/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="note note-primary">            <p>致谢：<br>本文所提供的方案全部由Toz提供，我将其整理为笔记，以方便其它中文用户的需要<br><a href="https://forum.xfce.org/viewtopic.php?id=18525">https://forum.xfce.org/viewtopic.php?id=18525</a></p>          </div><h2 id="问题"><a href="#问题" class="headerlink" title="问题"></a>问题</h2><p>thunar似乎默认不支持显示x11光标文件的缩略图，Toz提供了一个自定义缩略图的方案来解决这个问题</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>请确保以下软件包都安装了：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> pacman -S xcur2png imagemagick tumbler libxml2 libgepub libopenraw<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><h4 id="1-创建包含以下内容的文件-usr-share-thumbnailers-xcusrsor-thumbnailer："><a href="#1-创建包含以下内容的文件-usr-share-thumbnailers-xcusrsor-thumbnailer：" class="headerlink" title="1. 创建包含以下内容的文件/usr/share/thumbnailers/xcusrsor.thumbnailer："></a>1. 创建包含以下内容的文件<code>/usr/share/thumbnailers/xcusrsor.thumbnailer</code>：</h4><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-section">[Thumbnailer Entry]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">Version</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1.0</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">Encoding</span>=UTF-<span class="hljs-number">8</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">Type</span>=X-Thumbnailer<br><span class="hljs-attr">Name</span>=Xcursor Thumbnailer<br><span class="hljs-attr">MimeType</span>=image/x-xcursor<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">Exec</span>=/usr/local/bin/xcursorthumbs %i %o %s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-创建脚本-usr-local-bin-xcursorthumbs："><a href="#2-创建脚本-usr-local-bin-xcursorthumbs：" class="headerlink" title="2. 创建脚本/usr/local/bin/xcursorthumbs："></a>2. 创建脚本<code>/usr/local/bin/xcursorthumbs</code>：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-meta">#!/usr/bin/env bash</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> TEMP=$(<span class="hljs-built_in">mktemp</span> --directory --tmpdir tumbler-xcur-XXXXXX); <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span><br>xcur2png -d <span class="hljs-variable">$TEMP</span> -q -c - <span class="hljs-variable">$1</span> &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1<br>convert -thumbnail <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$3</span>&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$TEMP</span>/*_000.png&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$2</span>&quot;</span> &amp;&gt;/dev/null<br><span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -rf <span class="hljs-variable">$TEMP</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">fi</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-使脚本可执行："><a href="#3-使脚本可执行：" class="headerlink" title="3. 使脚本可执行："></a>3. 使脚本可执行：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> +x /usr/local/bin/xcursorthumbs<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="4-重启启动thunar和tumblerd"><a href="#4-重启启动thunar和tumblerd" class="headerlink" title="4.重启启动thunar和tumblerd"></a>4.重启启动thunar和tumblerd</h4><p>我选择直接重启：</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">reboot</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="效果"><a href="#效果" class="headerlink" title="效果"></a>效果</h2><p><img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2025/05/03/68155a867d89d.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
